---
/*
  This is not a layout but just a component that's used in page layouts.
  Easiest way to use a Google font is to embed it as a <link>. But we're
  gonna load fonts the fastest way.

  Here's the formula for best font load performance.
  1. Serve from same origin as woff/woff2
  2. Load font @font-face definitions as inline styles in page <head>
  3. Preload the same origin font URLs

  Hosting providers like Netlify/Vercel automatically cache your
  public assets (fonts) and serve from their CDN closest to the users.

  Read more here to understand font load performance
  https://sia.codes/posts/making-google-fonts-faster

  woff/woff2 assets downloaded using google-webfonts-helper:
  https://gwfh.mranftl.com/fonts/open-sans?subsets=latin
*/
---

<Fragment>
  <link rel="preload" href="/fonts/inter/inter-v12-latin-regular.woff2" as="font" type="font/woff2" crossorigin="crossorigin" />
  <link rel="preload" href="/fonts/inter/inter-v12-latin-500.woff2" as="font" type="font/woff2" crossorigin="crossorigin" />
  <link rel="preload" href="/fonts/inter/inter-v12-latin-700.woff2" as="font" type="font/woff2" crossorigin="crossorigin" />
  <link rel="preload" href="/fontawesome/webfonts/fa-brands-400.woff2" as="font" type="font/woff2" crossorigin="crossorigin" />
  <link rel="preload" href="/fontawesome/webfonts/fa-solid-900.woff2" as="font" type="font/woff2" crossorigin="crossorigin" />
  <style is:inline>
    /* inter-regular - latin */
    @font-face {
      font-family: Inter;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-style: normal;
      font-display: swap;

      /* regular name, postscript name, server url */
      src: local('Inter Regular'), local('Inter-Regular'), url('/fonts/inter/inter-v12-latin-regular.woff2') format('woff2');
    }

    /* inter-500 - latin */
    @font-face {
      font-family: Inter;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-style: normal;
      font-display: swap;

      /* regular name, postscript name, server url */
      src: local('Inter Medium'), local('Inter-Medium'), url('/fonts/inter/inter-v12-latin-500.woff2') format('woff2');
    }

    /* inter-700 - latin */
    @font-face {
      font-family: Inter;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-style: normal;
      font-display: swap;

      /* regular name, postscript name, server url */
      src: local('Inter Bold'), local('Inter-Bold'), url('/fonts/inter/inter-v12-latin-700.woff2') format('woff2');
    }
  </style>
  <link href="/fontawesome/css/bareminimum.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</Fragment>
